title: A Very Special Christmas Discography - 10 Albums
description:
A Very Special Christmas - Complete Discography as of 2013

Here is my present to the torrent community: The Complete Discography of the "A Very Special Christmas" album series. This collection contains all ten discs in the A Very Special Christmas Series, released as of December 2013. All songs are IDTagged for album, artist, track, and title. This is a great collection to load up on all of your shiny new gadgets and enjoy during this special time of year. All files are in MP3 format. The albums are as follows:

1987 A Very Special Christmas 1
1992 A Very Special Christmas 2
1997 A Very Special Christmas 3
1999 A Very Special Christmas Live
2001 A Very Special Christmas 5
2003 A Very Special Acoustic Christmas
2009 A Very Special Christmas 7
2012 A Very Special Christmas 25 Years
2012 A Very Special Christmas Peace on Earth
2013 ICON A Very Special Christmas 10

Merry Christmas Everyone!
